OCaml implementation of [RFC6287](http://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc6287) OCRA (OATH Challenge-Response Algorithm)
incl. [RFC Errata ID: 3729](http://www.rfc-editor.org/errata_search.php?eid=3729)
"""

